英国政府呼吁汽车制造商转产呼吸器，福特、本田、劳斯莱斯等多家车企正在接洽。
The British government is calling on car makers to switch to respirators, and a number of auto makers, including Ford, Honda and Rolls-Royce, are approaching.
侯卓铠。
